“You don’t have to act like a certain person or come from a certain place to reach your dreams.”

WNBA basketball player @emma_meesseman shows you can change the game without changing who you are.
 
2015 WNBA All-Star. 2019 WNBA Finals MVP. 6x Russian National League. 4x Euro League champion. Same baller from Ypres, Belgium. Whether she’s with her friends and family or traveling the world as a championship winner, Emma stays exactly who she is – just Emma. See how she brings new perspectives that prove you can fly high but stay rooted. 🚀🌳 

📹 @charlenevankasteren
📷 @Jaimygail
📷 @borislutters
